The Tap prompt allows users to pass signals to an application and any objects
belonging to the application. Interrupt a running app using ctl-c to open a
prompt, and any control signal to close.

usage:
  --/obj/signal *args

common signals:
  --//                   # list signals for app
  --//list               # list available objects
  --//help               # brings up this help
  --//tutorial           # brings up a brief tutorial

control signals: (use to close prompt)
  --//run                # resumes run
  --//stop               # stops after the current node
  --//terminate          # raises a terminate error
  --//exit               # exits immediately
  --//continue           # resumes run, opens a prompt on complete

object signals:
  --/obj/                # typically lists signals for obj
  --/obj/signal --help   # typically show help for signal
